                             THEME OF DARKWIND
----------------------------------------------------------------------
 
Darkwind's theme is one of medieval fantasy.  A place where swords and
sorcery meet to create an exciting but potentially lethal world for
brave adventurers to make a name for themselves.  You will not, nor
ever will find things from themes such as Science Fiction, Cybperpunk,
Comedy, Cartoons, Modern Day, etc.  We are dedicated to providing a
consistant environment where everything makes sense and blends well
together.  This rule will NEVER change, so if you would like to one
day aspire to become a wizard here, be warned now.  You will never
be allowed to place anything that doesn't fit into this theme into
the realm.

